---
title: Thai Beef Stir-Fry & Makrut Lime Rice with Roasted Peanuts & Cashews
description: Enjoy a medley of fragrant flavours in this stir-fry that uses Thai red curry paste for a gentle warming heat. With makrut lime leaves bringing an enticing aroma and roasted nuts for addictive crunch, this is an easy way to enjoy a taste of Thailand at home.

*Unfortunately, this week's courgette and Asian greens were in short supply, so we've replaced them with capsicum and baby spinach leaves. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-red-curry-stir-fry-ff3d91e1.jpg
